     - `shortcutsPublisher = $settings.map(\.application.shortcuts).removeDuplicates()`
     - `aiModelsPublisher = …`
   - `removeDuplicates()` + `Equatable` is the decoupling mechanism: editing a shortcut prompt never wakes up the hotkey listener.
